.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
Color: black, ebony, turquise, light-blood-red, blood-red
Nationality: colombian, dutch, chinese, polish, mexican
Cigar: swisher, dunhill, alhambra, blend, vegafina
Beverage: 7up, lemonade, juice, mirinda, iced-tea
Pet: pony, lizard, goldfish, ferret, cat

1. Nationality:colombian == Color:black
2. Nationality:dutch == Pet:pony
3. Beverage:7up == Color:ebony
4. Nationality:chinese == Beverage:lemonade
5. Color:ebony is to the right of Color:turquise
6. Cigar:swisher == Pet:cat
7. Cigar:dunhill == Color:light-blood-red
8. Beverage:juice is in the middle
9. Nationality:polish is on the far left
10. Cigar:alhambra is on the left or right of Pet:lizard
11. Cigar:dunhill is to the left or right of Pet:ferret
12. Cigar:blend == Beverage:mirinda
13. Nationality:mexican == Cigar:vegafina
14. Nationality:polish is to the left or right of Color:blood-red

.:: Answer ::.
